      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 h-auto gap-10 md:gap-20 py-10">
        <div class="static h-[385px] hidden md:block content-center">
          <img
            class="rounded-xl absolute md:w-[20rem] lg:w-[25rem] hover:z-40 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-105"
            src="/cycle-tour/roadbike/roadbike-trails-granada/rb-tg-3.webp"
            alt="ciclista mirando la sierra con cicicleta a su lado"
          />
          <img
            class="rounded-xl absolute md:w-[10rem] lg:w-[16rem] md:mt-48 lg:mt-60 ml-6 z-10 grayscale-[60%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-105"
            src="/cycle-tour/roadbike/roadbike-trails-granada/rb-tg-principal.webp"
            alt="ciclista mirando la sierra con cicicleta a su lado"
          />
          <img
            class="rounded-xl absolute md:w-[10rem] lg:w-[18em] ml-64 md:-mt-24 lg:-mt-32 grayscale-[60%] hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-300 ease-out hover:scale-105"
            src="/cycle-tour/roadbike/roadbike-trails-granada/rb-tg-1.webp"
            alt="ciclista mirando la sierra con cicicleta a su lado"
          />
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-5">
          <div class="">
            <h2
              class="max-w-2xl md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
              Availability
            </h2>
            <Dots class="mb-4" />

            <ul class="grid gap-2 text-lg">
              <li class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <Icon icon="spring-logo" size="1.6rem" color="#0E46A3" />
                <p>Spring / Autumn / Winter</p>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2
              class="max-w-2xl md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
              Highlight
            </h2>
            <Dots class="mb-4" />
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              Explore the Outdoors of Granada on your Road bike through an area
              with many landscapes from rolling hills, pine forests, deserts,
              and mountains to the tropical coast.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              Enjoy our rural hotel selected with great care for its location
              and character to make your trip a single experience.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="">
            <h2
              class="max-w-2xl md:px-0 font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl xl:text-6xl">
              Requirements
            </h2>
            <Dots class="mb-4" />
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> Cycling is an activity carrying some
              inherent risks. Please consider your skills, abilities, and fitness
              carefully, and always wear a helmet.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> The route type and difficulty are based
              on your fitness level and technical skills. Before booking the ‚ÄúRoad
              Bike Escape Granada,‚Äù please fill out a questionnaire form to tailor
              your itinerary to the right level.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> n your ROAD BIKE Questionnaire, you
              should submit honest information about your Road Bike experience, physical
              fitness, and comfort. We offer different trails for all levels to give
              you a positive and safe experience with us.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-900">
              <span class="text-xl">üîπ</span> If you are uncertain about what fitness
              level or technical difficulty is most appropriate for you, check our
              Blog Cycling article ‚ÄúCycle grades‚Äù or contact us.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-20 md:mt-14 items-center">
