        for the first day, the rides are organized in the morning, giving you
        time to relax in the afternoon while enjoying your rural accommodation.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        On the first day, we organize a route in the afternoon.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        There is the option to visit the city of Granada and explore the many
        cultural sites and countless tapa bars and restaurants. For those who
        would like to visit the Alhambra Palace, there is the option to organize
        the tour on the last day in the morning.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        Being a tour of 4 days, the Road Bike Escape Granada is designed for
        those who need a break and want to take a few days off looking for some
        great riding.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        For non-riding partners, we organize extra activities during your stay.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        Easy to get to Granada by our organized transport either in the airport
        M√°laga or Granada.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        We have extensive knowledge of all the trails and tailor each ride to
        the guests to ensure you a great experience with us.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-lg mt-4 md:px-4">
        Join us and experience our cycle routes, an ideal place to challenge
        yourself and experience epic bicycle routes through the province.
      </p>
    </main>
  </Container>
